<i>verb</i>: 펼치다 [펼치다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>펼치다 [펼치다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. open; spread out</dd><br>
<dd>펴서 드러내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To open and expose something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unfold; unroll; spread out</dd><br>
<dd>접히거나 포개진 것을 넓게 펴다.</dd><br>
<dd>For something folded or overlapped to be spread widely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. present</dd><br>
<dd>보고 듣거나 즐길 수 있도록 사람들 앞에 관심을 집중시킬 만한 상태로 나타내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To express something in an interesting manner, so that people can watch, listen to, or enjoy it.</dd><br>
<dd>4. realize; carry out</dd><br>
<dd>꿈이나 계획 등을 실제로 행하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To put a dream, plan, etc., into action.</dd><br>
<dd>5. develop</dd><br>
<dd>생각 등을 전개하거나 발전시키다.</dd><br>
<dd>To expand or build up a thought, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>